HIV pixel clustering - fewer markers

Candace Liu

January 18, 2021

  • Gaussian blur sigma=2, k=20 (pixel metaclusters)
  • z-score cap=3 for hierarchical clustering
  • For each pixel, divide each marker by total (each pixel sums to 1)
  • Markers: CD14,CD209,CD16,HLA-DR-DQ-DP,MPO,CD3,SMA,CD11c,CD68,CD138,CD45,CD21,CD20,CD163,CD206,CD31
